    <with|font-series|bold|Maschine Learning:> Machine learning is concerned
    with the development of algorithms and techniques, which allow computers
    to "learn". At a general level, there are two types of learning:
    inductive, and deductive. Inductive machine learning methods create
    computer programs by extracting rules and patterns out of massive data
    sets.

    <\itemize-dot>
